WEBVTT

00:02.029 --> 00:04.910
<i>Deep within the
bleak and dismal gowanus canal,</i>

00:04.910 --> 00:07.860
<i>hidden beneath its murky
waters, lies the headquarters</i>

00:07.860 --> 00:10.920
<i>of the most sinister
crime collective in New York ...</i>

00:10.920 --> 00:12.700
<i>the Doom Factory.</i>

00:12.700 --> 00:16.540
<i>Here, 10 of the most ruthlessly
self-involved villains on Earth</i>

00:16.540 --> 00:19.770
<i>loosely align forces against
the powers of good.</i>

00:19.780 --> 00:24.180
<i>The cold-hearted ice
sculptress, Frigid.</i>

00:24.180 --> 00:26.010
The toxic tongue of Serpentine.

00:26.020 --> 00:30.300
Oh, look everyone. Poor little
rich girl needs attention.

00:30.300 --> 00:34.720
<i>Miniature muse Eenie-Meanie
and Gerard the gorilla.</i>

00:34.720 --> 00:36.470
<i>The watchful Black Maria,</i>

00:36.480 --> 00:38.980
<i>and Trashenstein,
the exquisite corpse.</i>

00:38.980 --> 00:42.110
<i>Ultra-Violent and Billy Maim.</i>

00:42.120 --> 00:44.230
<i>The feminine-yet-gigantic
She-Hemoth</i>

00:44.230 --> 00:46.870
<i>and the bittersweet Hard Candy...</i>

00:46.870 --> 00:48.820
<i>all sycophantic clingers-on</i>

00:48.820 --> 00:51.910
<i>to the evil genius of
Wes Warhammer.</i>

00:51.910 --> 00:55.740
Hey, so, um, uh, guys, um...

00:55.750 --> 00:58.250
we should get Dr. Venture.

01:00.000 --> 01:06.074
